Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天色不太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雨之前先找个地方投宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这阵雾气是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不清路了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加代夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪异 被诅咒的幽灵城
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密之国大名夫人加代正在回国的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是国人久候未见 于是便去迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可山道之上只见轿子的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人及其随从都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说要找到夫人阁下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人没什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但雏田的白眼 牙和赤丸的嗅觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是搜索任务的得力助手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆怎么能这么讲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就没有一点可取之处了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为鸣人是有自己的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我的优点说给婆婆听听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说吧说吧 我的优点是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…那个…我认为是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这跟没说有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个有完没完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说婆婆 这个任务有什么内幕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,内幕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…也就是幽灵什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵 你怕它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那么一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会有幽灵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡说 快点出发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是出发去哪儿呢 火影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首崎岭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首…你说首…就是脖子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是不好的预感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身为忍者怎么能害怕这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我出发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她比幽灵可怕多了 会吃人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这家伙总让我头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首崎岭曾经是首之国的首都吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五十年前灭亡的首崎一族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:05:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的城堡应该还在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一座空城而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人的胆小传染给你了吗 静音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首崎岭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得不是个好兆头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好 下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越下越大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有听说过这里修建过城堡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好阴森啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越看越是个不祥的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:06:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定那儿有什么重要的线索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呆在这里全身都被淋湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很宏伟的城堡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是打搅到人家怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天色已晚 真是麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你真怕这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大胆点 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,门自动开了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了 有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面的灯亮着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想在这里躲躲雨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香的气味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是热的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才有人来过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面相可怕的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是这个城堡的城主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城主的话就是大名了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是大名的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那这一带应该就是某国的首都了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是这里是国境啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃坏肚子怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才画上的眼睛动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 画怎么会动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你紧张过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个饭桌有七人份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失踪的密之国一行也是七个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许夫人他们还在这个城堡里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分头找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要分头找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难得有机会大家一起行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 牙 雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要小孩子气到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是任务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生什么气吗 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种场合真不适合我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比夜里一个人上厕所还恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牙 雏田 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人果然不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也感觉到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实是人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁 谁在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天井
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《首崎城纪事》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五十年前的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城池已经被敌人包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人民惨遭蹂躏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城内弹尽粮绝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今夜后 吾虽亡 却不得瞑目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾辈之怨 余留城内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:11:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心系此城而尽毁入城者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首崎刚佐书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首崎刚佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雏田 醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牙 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五十年前沦陷的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卷轴所署的日期是五十年前的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面说要吞噬一切入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的确被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和首崎家的铠甲不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道这是敌人的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对面也有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个铠甲是首崎家的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是快点离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和那幅画里一样的铠甲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道他就是首崎刚佐本人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首崎刚佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好刺鼻的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个城堡的确很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墙壁四周分布着查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个墙壁像活的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柔拳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我见过类似的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人召唤的蛤蟆胃就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胃里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这个气味 是胃酸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首崎刚佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在城池被攻陷前召唤了它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他召唤的东西吞噬了整个城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从进入这个城堡开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就已经是它是午餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要特意变成城堡的样子来吃我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密之国的大名夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被墙壁困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是木叶的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就救你们出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙想把所有的人都集中到这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后一起解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去我们就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 雏田我们出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兽人分身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牙通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾乃城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奉刚佐大人之命 入城者必死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么才能从这里出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然是通灵之物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就应该有契约卷轴之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毁了它 这家伙就会回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面 应该在天守那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是该怎么上去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墙壁的查克拉又安定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首崎刚佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可别再上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定他是通灵兽制造的幻像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 和刚才有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像让我们跟着他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卷轴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又开始发疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通灵兽的本体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酸的浓度增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点解决它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么送它回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可能也会一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听天由命吧 博一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 那里应该是突破点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 影分身术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城主含着对侵略者的怨念死去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他却把我们带到了卷轴那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说城主的怨念已经散了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且五十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也希望一直守护这里的通灵兽可以回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能城主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直等着能解放通灵兽的人到来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.28,0:20:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任务完成 可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浓眉 结果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.58,0:22:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样子很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他或许受到打击了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诊断结果肯定不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且相当的不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相当的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无可奈何 一定非常严重
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道浓眉会…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:22:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.78,0:22:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:22:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相当的…相当的严重…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.68,0:23:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三超兽 最大的对手